            <li><strong>Explanation sentence:</strong> This means that Allah is not like creation and that all creation depends on Him.</li>
            <li><strong>Importance sentence:</strong> This is important for Muslims because it strengthens Tawhid, protects them from shirk and helps them rely on Allah in worship and hardship.</li>
          </ul>
